ura.io/ipfs/Qmaxy3rHUzZCPFPjm5yLzahhbeYZPnBCNDZ8rjca81c1Mt?filename=GOOwKun.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGOOwKun.png&h=1a4b02dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeNwY9foZhiDGsfqgRhgYo2gokVgBtN782G7zzoQFf8Bc?filename=nRQWa9o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnRQWa9o.png&h=45949141&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZa6MML4sProMPm5ws6esaABSrBp1fRpiw2ZRWXqfuuxB?filename=9kqK4uo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9kqK4uo.png&h=5cf82730&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>點樣教大視窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n將電腦既解像度較低<br />\n<br />\n地圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201710/ad03db1a0a037d79f8063e8253656fa1.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201710%2Fad03db1a0a037d79f8063e8253656fa1.JPG&h=a9858ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n揀職可睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=70151&amp;snA=151&amp;bpage=1&amp;ltype=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D70151%26snA%3D151%26bpage%3D1%26ltype%3D&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=04eef213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=70151&amp;snA=151&amp;bpage=1&amp;ltype=</a><br />\n<br />\n有用網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://cgsword.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcgsword.com%2F&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVpkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=a6a0a797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cgsword.com/</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/G1.php?bsn=2577\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com